
scripts for creating SLES12 schroot images

* bootstrap-buildroot:
    * bootstraps a chroot image for SLES12
    * needs to be run as root on an SLES12 system
    * produces a tarball: sles12-buildroot.tar.bz2

* create-buildroot-lv:
    * creates a buildroot template LV from tarball
    * needs to be run as root
    * tarball needs to exist: sles12-buildroot.tar.bz2

* setup-schroot
    * install schroot config for the builder chroot
